New:           
CopyVerify - Copy files like "Copy" do but verify that source and destination are the same
             a summery is shown at the end
Cutfile - cuts a file you can give newname, start and how many bytes to cut. No Special Settings.
Joinfile - Join two files together, you can give a new filename. No Special Settings.

